
-# Conditional Blocks
- if @person.trusteenumber == "One"
  I name #{@person.trusteetheone} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteetheone} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name the person whom the majority of the beneficiaries under this Will choose or whomever the court deems fit to be my personal representative. 
- elsif @person.trusteenumber == "Two"
  I name #{@person.trusteetheone} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteetheone} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethesecond} as my personal representative and guardian of my children. If #{@person.trusteethesecond} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name the person whom the majority of the beneficiaries under this Will choose or whomever the court deems fit to be my personal representative.
- elsif @person.trusteenumber == "Three"
  I name #{@person.trusteetheone} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteetheone} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethesecond} as my personal representative and guardian of my children. If #{@person.trusteethesecond} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethethird} as my personal representative and guardian of my children. If #{@person.trusteethethird} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name the person whom the majority of the beneficiaries under this Will choose or whomever the court deems fit to be my personal representative.
- elsif @person.trusteenumber == "Four"
  If neither of us can serve as trustee because of resignation, incapacity, or death, we name #{@person.trustee.single_successor_trustee} as our successor trustee. If #{@person.trustee.single_successor_trustee} is unable or unwilling to serve, we name #{@person.trustee.second_successor_trustee} as our successor trustee. If #{@person.trustee.second_successor_trustee} is unable or unwilling to serve, we name #{@person.trustee.third_successor_trustee} as our successor trustee. If #{@person.trustee.third_successor_trustee} is unable or unwilling to serve, we name #{@person.trustee.fourth_successor_trustee} as our successor trustee. If #{@person.trustee.fourth_successor_trustee} is unable or unwilling to serve, we direct the successor trustee to be chosen according to Section 5.11 of this trust.
- elsif @person.trusteenumber == "Five"
  I name #{@person.trusteetheone} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteetheone} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethesecond} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteethesecond} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethethird} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteethethird} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethefourth} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteethefourth} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name #{@person.trusteethefifth} as my personal representative. If #{@person.trusteethefifth} is unable or unwilling to serve, I name the person whom the majority of the beneficiaries under this Will choose or whomever the court deems fit to be my personal representative.

